    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You increase your brain activity, stimulating your memory and allowing you to explore your memory thoroughly. You gain a +4 insight bonus to all saves and checks that relate to events you have experienced in the past (for example, to help gather clues or form a conclusion based on reviewing memories of the investigation) (GM's discretion).<br><br>This technique can only be used once per day, and once it ends you become @Condition[fatigued]{fatigued}. You also take 1d6 temporary Intelligence damage (Fortitude DC 18 negates).</p>\n\n\n\n",
